title: Traffic update: Two lanes closed at Dartford Tunnel | Meridian
text:
Two lanes closed and queueing traffic due to broken down vehicle and recovery work on M25 Dartford Tunnel anticlockwise between J1A A206 / A226 (Erith / Swanscombe) and J31 A1306 (West Thurrock), congestion on M25 to J2 A2 (Darenth Interchange).
Broken down vehicle in the right-hand East Bore tunnel.
Last updated Sat 24 Oct 2015 Travel Kent
